item.title: CVE-2019-10373|2024-08-04T22:17:20.409Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20build%20pipeline%20plugin
item.description: A stored cross-site scripting vulnerability in Jenkins Build Pipeline Plugin 1.5.8 and earlier allows attackers able to edit the build pipeline description to inject arbitrary HTML and JavaScript in the plugin-provided web pages in Jenkins.
